videos.description: Iowa's Tarique Milton attempts to return the punt but has the ball stripped by Alohi Gilman and Chase Claypool makes the fumble recovery.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Notre Dame's Gilman causes fumble on punt return) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Notre Dame's Gilman causes fumble on punt return

videos.description: Brock Purdy tries to scramble out of the pocket  but Jeremiah Owusu-Koramoah knocks the ball free and recovers the fumble for Notre Dame's second fumble recovery of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Notre Dame forces second fumble of the game) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Notre Dame forces second fumble of the game

videos.description: Ian Book lobs a pass to Chase Claypool who leaps into the air to make an exciting 24-yard touchdown catch to give Notre Dame a 10-0 lead over Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Claypool climbs the ladder for impressive TD grab) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Claypool climbs the ladder for impressive TD grab

videos.description: Chase Claypool makes a catch but comes up short on his dive for the end zone. Then Jafar Armstrong takes the handoff to score from the one-yard line to give Notre Dame a 20-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Claypool's diving effort sets up Armstrong's TD for Notre Dame) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Claypool's diving effort sets up Armstrong's TD for Notre Dame

videos.description: Brock Purdy suffers a leg injury after being sacked as he tries to escape the pocket and requires the assistance of his teammates to get off the field.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdy limps off the field after being sacked) 2019/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdy limps off the field after being sacked
